acking:</strong></p><p>Our versatile paper bags are perfect for gifting homemade treats or packing gifts neatly and beautifully.</p><p><strong>Personalised Paper Bags:</strong></p><p>Add a personal touch to your gifts with our customisable paper bags, making your presents truly unique.</p><p><strong>Easy to Use:</strong></p><p>Our paper is easy to cut, fold, and tape, providing a hassle-free wrapping experience.</p><p><strong>Why should everyone use Deli Paper\'s gift wrap paper?</strong></p><p>Deli Paper recognises the significance of presentation when it comes to gift-giving. Our gift wrapping paper is intended to make your gifts stand out and show your loved ones how much you care. Whether you\'re wrapping a modest token or a large gift, our paper provides that particular touch.</p><p>Our gift\'s wrapping material is both useful and creative. Use it to create personalised wrapping paper, birthday wrapping paper, or present wrapping paper. Its adaptability makes it ideal for making gift bags, wrapping paper, and other products. The luxury look and feel elevate any gift.</p><p>Discover the beauty and versatility of Deli Paper\'s gift wrapping paper. Available in rolls and sheets, it fits seamlessly into your gift-giving routine, making every present memorable and elegant.</p><p>Add a roll to your cart today and see why Deli Paper\'s gift wrapping paper is the perfect choice for every occasion.</p>', '1747464681_1135_3a_81b42ece-52a1-4b11-b344-88056a615b3e_1625x1613.webp', '1747418440_8685_gift_paper_2.jpg', '', 'Elegant Gift Wrapping Paper, Perfect for Every Occasion', 'Discover our collection of exquisite gift wrapping papers, designed to add a touch of elegance to your presents. Eco-friendly materials and stylish designs .', '', 'active', '2025-04-21 12:50:49', '2025-05-26 02:09:56', 'yes');
INSERT INTO `product` (`product_id`, `product_name`, `product_url`, `product_short_description`, `product_content`, `product_thumbnail`, `product_image1`, `product_image2`, `product_meta_title`, `product_meta_description`, `product_meta_keywords`, `product_status`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `product_index`) VALUES ('5', 'Paper Bags', 'cutom-paper-bags-in-uk', 'Embrace sustainability with our eco-friendly paper bags, designed to meet your everyday packaging needs while reducing environmental impact. Crafted from responsibly sourced materials, these paper bags offer a perfect blend of durability, functionality, and eco-consciousness.', '<ol><li><strong>Environmentally Responsible Production</strong></li></ol><p>Crafted from renewable resources, our&nbsp;<strong>paper bags</strong>&nbsp;help reduce reliance on single-use plastics, contributing to a cleaner planet. Manufactured using sustainable practices, ensuring minimal environmental footprint throughout the production process.</p><ol><li><strong>Robust and Reliable Construction</strong></li></ol><p>Engineered with high-quality paper materials, our&nbsp;<strong>paper bags</strong>&nbsp;are designed to withstand the rigors of everyday use, offering exceptional strength and durability. Reinforced handles provide added support, making these&nbsp;<strong>paper bags</strong>&nbsp;ideal for carrying groceries, merchandise, or personal belongings with ease.</p><ol><li><strong>Versatile Usage for Various Applications</strong></li></ol><p>From retail shopping to event giveaways, these versatile&nbsp;<strong>paper bags</strong>&nbsp;are suitable for a wide range of purposes, catering to both business and personal needs. Perfect for packaging goods, organizing items, or presenting gifts in an eco-friendly and stylish manner.</p><ol><li><strong>Customizable Options for Branding</strong></li></ol><p>Elevate your brand presence with custom printing or branding options available for our&nbsp;<strong>paper bags</strong>. Personalize each bag with your logo, slogan, or artwork to enhance brand recognition and create a lasting impression on customers.</p><ol><li><strong>Biodegradable and Recyclable</strong></li></ol><p>After use, our&nbsp;<strong>paper bags</strong>&nbsp;can be easily recycled or composted, minimizing waste and promoting a circular economy. Biodegradable materials ensure that even if disposed of improperly, these&nbsp;<strong>paper bags</strong>&nbsp;will naturally break down over time, leaving no harmful residue behind.</p>', '1747332679_9554_custom_w_paper_bags.jpg', '1747418440_1814_paper_bag_1.jpg', '', 'Deli Paper Premium Paper Bags are a Step Above the Rest', 'Deli Paper offers eco-friendly paper bags that are perfect for any occasion. Ideal for food packaging, shopping and more, these bags are durable', '', 'active', '2025-04-21 12:50:54', '2025-05-19 09:29:59', 'yes');
